# Stock Price Prediction (Short-Term)

## Objective
Predict next day closing price using historical stock data.

## Dataset
Yahoo Finance data using yfinance library.

## Features Used
- Open
- High
- Low
- Volume

## Models Applied
- Linear Regression
- Random Forest

## Results
- Random Forest performed better than Linear Regression.
- Model captured trend but struggled with sudden changes.

## Tools Used
- Python
- Google Colab
- scikit-learn
- yfinance
